db.mycoll.insert(Array.from({length: 4}, (_, i) => ({_id: i, a: i})))
db.mycoll.createIndex({a: 1}, {unique: true})
{code}

and run this Node.js code sample (courtesy of [~max.hirschhorn]):
 
{code:javascript}
